About this item

  • Dual Monitor Stand – Designed to mount 17” to 32” computer monitor screens, this two-monitor stand lets you find a comfortable, ergonomic viewing height to relieve neck and back tension and improve natural posture.
  • Adjustable Tension and Stability – Each arm monitor stand holds up to 17.6 lbs. each and features an adjustable, built-in gas spring tension gauge to help better manage your PC screen and keep it firmly in place.
  • Multiple Viewing Angles – A free-tilting design that lets you view each screen vertically or horizontally, enjoy 360° screen rotation, a tilt range of +/- 35°, and a swivel range of +/- 90° to help you get the perfect angle.
  • Convenient Cable Management – This computer monitor stand helps save space on your desktop by removing the tabletop monitor stands and keeping cords and cables neatly organized along the arms.
  • Dual Mounting Options – The detachable VESA plate provides easier installation while the dual mounting options let you choose between a desk clamp or grommet to better suit your home or office desktop.
